resourcefalseldap_read resourcelink_identifier stringbase_dn stringfilter arrayattributesarray("*") intattrsonly0 intsizelimit-1 inttimelimit-1 intderefLDAP_DEREF_NEVER arrayserverctrlsarray()
Performs the search for a specified filter on the directory with the scope LDAP_SCOPE_BASE. So it is equivalent to reading an entry from the directory.

